data.description:
Concession!!! $5,000.00 so you can buy your own appliances and carpet or closing cost.  Great Location and rare opportunity to make your home your own!  Pool in the front yard, plenty of grass to play and relax.  Spacious backyard is fenced with a covered patio for enjoying the sunset and entertaining.  Behind unit within walking distance is dog park and walking trails. On RTD bus route, close to Downtown Littleton, light rail and Arapahoe Community College.  New roof, some new paint, new ceiling upstairs, foundation improvement to support new roof, new water heater, and new fireplace.  Needs some TLC, but the bones are solid.  Sold as-is.
Call Ruth Gonce 303-905-1001 to setup a showing.
